'''Acarophilia''' is a [[paraphilia]] consisting of sexual arousal from scratching.<ref>{{cite book| last=Hickey| first=Eric W.|publisher= Pearson Education| year=2006| page= 87| title=Sex crimes and Paraphilia}}</ref><ref name=aggrawal09>{{cite book | pages=369, 375 |title=Forensic and Medico-legal Aspects of Sexual Crimes and Unusual Sexual Practices |first=Anil |last=Aggrawal |publisher=CRC Press |location=Boca Raton|year=2009|ISBN=978-1-4200-4308-2}}</ref>{{rp|369}} Although it is often confused with arousal from tickling ([[knismolagnia]]), they are listed as distinct paraphilias in scientific literature.<ref name=aggrawal09 />{{rp|375}}

